HEADWORD: Inconsummate
<hw>In`con*sum"mate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inconsummatus</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not, and
<er>Consummate</er>.]</ety> <def>Not consummated; not finished;
incomplete.</def> <au>Sir M. Hale.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>In`con*sum"mate*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

